    thinking: "**Confirming The Name**\n\nI\'m thrilled; the app name, \"MoodFit,\" is a perfect fit. I\'ve been reviewing the finished UI, specifically how custom color constants in Color.kt for the \"Vibrant Palette\" theme are. I focused on primary, background, surface, and pastel accent colors to ensure they all work together in harmony. Solid\n\n\n"
    modified_response: "I have completed the refactoring of \"MoodFit\" to present the design instructions of the **Vibrant Palette** with a high-fidelity visual experience:\n\n### \360\237\216\250 Visual & Layout Enhancements Implemented\n- **Vibrant Interactive Header**: Updated the top banner with an uppercase minimalist welcome subhead. Built specialized 48dp circular capsule buttons for the **Light/Dark Toggle (\342\230\200\357\270\217 / \360\237\214\231)** and the **OAuth Account Synced Profile (\360\237\221\244 / \342\234\205)**, adding beautiful tactile interactive feedback.\n- **Translucent Mood Card Grid**: Upgraded the mood picker from basic choice widgets into a stunning translucent custom-styled grid mimicking the mockup aesthetics. Selected moods glow with bold brand highlights (`#6750A4` / `#D0BCFF`), while the non-selected rest as soft glass surfaces. Kept a seamless collapsable \"Testing Panel\" inside the card containing the standard dropdown and radio indicators to preserve 100% test scenario compatibility.\n- **Micro UI Accents**: Added the premium `AI GEN` status capsule pill in the suggested activities list header to elevate the design.\n- **Polished Card Architecture (`ActivitySuggestionCard`)**: Refactored suggestion templates to match modern card systems:\n  - **Dynamic Pastel Emoji Canvas**: Each recommendation displays a custom theme square (`\360\237\247\230` for Mindfulness, `\360\237\216\247` for Ambient Audio, `\360\237\223\235` for Journaling, `\360\237\232\266` for exercise) wrapped inside alternating pastel hues (e.g., Soft Pink, Lilac, Mint, Lavender) that shift color depending on the mood category.\n  - **Premium State Icons**: Updated save states to dynamic solid micro hearts (`\342\231\245\357\270\217` vs `\342\231\241`).\n  - **Clean Segment Chips**: Unified styling for categories and type chips in cozy mini-badges alongside streamlined button handlers for **Google Calendar** matching Material Design layout standards.\n- **Custom Tab Layouts**: Added specific brand styling to the Bottom Navigation Bar, forcing dynamic colors to lock to custom primary schemes for active indicators.\n"
    thinking_duration {
      seconds: 1
      nanos: 503929295
    }
    stop_reason: STOP_REASON_STOP_PATTERN
  }
}
